<div class="com-share" data-id="1873" data-title="《想当编剧的广电总局不想让小三有幸福》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/1873/medium/1873.jpg?1436646333" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/1873?spm=0.0.0.0.FdDwmz" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
